# RQ-53-20-03-150: Visual Inspection Pre-flight

## Requirement Statement
The BWB outer skin panels shall be visually inspectable for damage during pre-flight walk-around inspection.

## Rationale
Early detection of impact damage, surface defects, or delamination.

## Acceptance Criteria
- All panel surfaces visible from ground or access platform
- Damage criteria defined in AMM (visible damage > 25mm)
- Lighting adequate for inspection
- Inspection time < 15 minutes (all panels)

## Compliance Status
Inspection procedure drafted

## Traceability
Parent: AMM Chapter 53-20
